I am a User Experience Researcher with doctoral training in Experimental Psychology. I leverage my research training to ensure human centered-design and provide a seamless user experience.

As a User Experience Researcher:

- I empathize and advocate for the user.
- I choose the right methods to gain insight into users' mental models and uncover critical usability - issues and potential pain points.
- I hone in on the most important findings and persuasively deliver design recommendations.
- I support and empower designers and product management teams through research insights.
